This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on providing insights for robotic researchers. It also discusses visual processing for action, which is relevant to robotics. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper discusses human visual understanding. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses cognitive processing. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses hierarchical processing and anticipatory nature of visual processing, which are relevant to these fields.
